    "body": "See your error message, you're getting a `revert` in your transaction. The reason is that you're passing invalid parameters to your `Crowdsale`, which [has some validations in its constructor](https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-solidity/blob/v1.12.0/contracts/crowdsale/Crowdsale.sol#L58).\r\n\r\nMake sure the `rate`, `wallet` and `token` parameters are valid, and you'll be able to deploy just fine.",
